WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:06.400
Good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:07.919
joining us again tonight. We're

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:10.000
going to go over some of the news, but

00:00:07.919 --> 00:00:12.800
first, I'll go over what the Lord showed

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.599
us in prayer last night.

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:18.480
I have to say, out of all

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:20.720
the prayers we've had in the last

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:22.400
year, for some of the things

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:25.038
the Lord showed us, I think it was

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:26.320
one of the top ones I've seen in a

00:00:25.039 --> 00:00:29.039
while.

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:33.120
I wasn't anticipating

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:35.200
that. I just come in,

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:37.839
pray and yield, and the Lord

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:40.640
shows you things.

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:43.280
There's a lot to it, so I'll go into

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:48.879
some of it. I won't go into all of it,

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:51.760
but I'll go into some of it.

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:54.760
I don't even know where to start.

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:06.479
I saw the White House. I saw President

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:09.840
Trump. We were praying for Paula

00:01:06.479 --> 00:01:11.600
White. That's how it all started. We

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:14.640
started praying for Paula White and her

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:16.080
health and just her in general,

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:18.720
because the Lord put it on my heart,

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:22.159
too.

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:24.240
Then all of a sudden,

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:26.080
I started praying for the French Quarter

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:29.679
again.

00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:32.720
We saw the red, white, and blue

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:35.520
concerning the French flag—the red,

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:38.560
white, and blue for an attack in the

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:42.000
French Quarter again. Last

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:44.720
time I saw an African-American

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:47.680
woman walking down the streets of

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:50.158
New Orleans and Bourbon Street.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:54.320
She had red, white, and

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:57.520
blue glitter on her skin, and she had

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:59.119
glasses that said 250.

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:02.079
They looked like those big ones you

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:05.680
get at New York Times Square for

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:08.239
the New Year, but it looked like 250 on

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:12.160
her glasses. She was walking down

00:02:08.239 --> 00:02:15.280
the main street, and I saw a

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:18.799
device in an old building in the French

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:23.920
Quarter. It went off and

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:26.319
looked like it was a gas leak, but it

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:29.599
wasn't a gas leak; it was intentional, by

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:33.040
a remote. As I've prayed into that,

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:36.079
I still have a caution to pray

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:39.679
over New Orleans. I saw red, white, and blue again last

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:42.800
night, and I

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:45.040
saw the French Quarter again.

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:49.040
I thought that was interesting, but

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:50.640
it went on from there. I saw

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:59.760
J.D. Vance with five keys

00:02:55.280 --> 00:03:04.400
in his hand—five keys on a big circle

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:07.920
keychain. They were all skeleton keys,

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:12.000
and each key was different.

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:15.760
Some of them were small, and the

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:19.280
design at the end of the key looked like

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:22.799
something out of a pirate movie, like an

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:25.760
old skeleton key; it

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:29.519
was very elaborate. The design at the

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:32.720
end of every key was

00:03:29.519 --> 00:03:35.599
very special.

00:03:32.720 --> 00:03:38.640
They didn't look like a normal skeleton

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:40.640
key with just a little piece

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:43.040
of metal

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:45.040
on the end; every key was

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:47.359
very elaborate.

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:50.720
They were beautiful-looking keys.

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:53.680
Some of them looked very medieval.

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:55.680
Some

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:57.760
looked evil, but they were pretty

00:03:55.680 --> 00:04:00.239
in their

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:03.840
designs and calligraphy.

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:06.239
One key was

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:09.840
black and white, another

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:13.280
was gold, and another

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:15.200
was silver with some tarnish on it, looking

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:19.199
like tarnished stainless steel.

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:21.519
Another key was

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:23.360
polished at the end, but the further it

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:27.360
went down to the

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:30.720
part that opens the lock, it was very dark. Each of

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:33.040
the five keys

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:36.000
represented something different. He

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:39.040
had the five keys on a keychain and

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:42.240
was looking at

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:46.080
all five of

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:48.639
them. As I was looking at J.D. Vance, he was

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:52.560
coming out of a

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:55.440
big box.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:58.479
You could see his fingers

00:04:55.440 --> 00:05:01.199
coming out of the top. The

00:04:58.479 --> 00:05:03.440
lid was off now,

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:05.919
and he was creeping out,

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:07.840
coming out of the box of who he

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:10.960
truly is and

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:14.799
what's really inside of him.

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:17.359
I saw

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:19.280
the French Quarter and

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:21.680
some things I can't talk about,

00:05:19.280 --> 00:05:26.400
especially with an

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:28.160
individual, but I heard from

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:33.120
the Lord

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:37.280
about

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:41.600
the Louisiana Purchase. As I

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:44.880
saw the Louisiana Purchase,

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:47.840
I

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:55.880
heard the Lord say, 'Covenants made,

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:55.880
covenants kept.

00:05:55.919 --> 00:05:58.880
Covenants made, covenants kept, but you

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:01.840
didn't keep yours.'He

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:05.120
made covenants

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:10.240
and

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:12.240
kept his side of it, but you

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:15.280
didn't keep yours. He's talking about

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:20.479
the United States. I saw a massive oak

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:23.840
tree come up out of Louisiana.

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:28.400
This major oak tree

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:31.359
was alive; it

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:36.479
had waves to it and was moving before

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:41.840
my eyes. It had 250 on the

00:06:36.479 --> 00:06:46.719
leaves.

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:50.159
I saw the old Catholic church

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:53.680
in New Orleans that has the horse rider

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:57.039
in front. I didn't realize that

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:58.639
was a Civil War monument. Based

00:06:57.039 --> 00:07:00.719
on what I understand from

00:06:58.639 --> 00:07:04.800
Diana's research,

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:08.479
this is the

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:12.400
oldest active Catholic church

00:07:08.479 --> 00:07:14.960
in America. It's

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:18.159
the oldest church that still holds weekly services;

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:20.880
that's

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:23.280
what Diana told me. I saw that beautiful

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:26.319
church near the

00:07:23.280 --> 00:07:28.559
Mississippi River.

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:35.360
The Lord was showing me that church.

00:07:31.599 --> 00:07:38.479
Out of it came a

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:40.720
single

00:07:38.479 --> 00:07:42.000
candlestick—a

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:44.400
beautiful candle. There was only one

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:46.560
candle there. It was in a candlestick holder made out of olive wood. It was beautiful, with different colors, and it

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:49.440
ring for

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:52.160
your finger

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:10.240
so you could carry it.

00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:16.879
Suddenly,

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:21.720
Mother Mary came out of the Catholic

00:08:16.879 --> 00:08:21.720
church. This is very interesting.

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:30.720
I'm going to describe the

00:08:28.479 --> 00:08:32.559
way I saw Mother

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:38.560
Mary. She

00:08:32.559 --> 00:08:41.359
wasn't a shrine

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:43.359
or a

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:46.480
statue; she

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:49.279
was real.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:52.720
She had a blue head covering

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:55.279
on, like

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:57.680
a modesty

00:08:55.279 --> 00:09:03.040
veil.

00:08:57.680 --> 00:09:07.359
It was blue and white, similar to the

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:09.680
Jewish flag. It had blue, white, and gold, like you see on a rabbi's prayer shawls with

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:12.560
the

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:19.279
knots.

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:25.959
She was wearing the same colors.

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:32.640
She looked like a young woman.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:38.640
I'm

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:42.640
not trying to be disrespectful, but

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:46.880
she was not traditionally beautiful, nor

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:49.920
was she ugly.

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:56.880
She looked humble and

00:09:52.800 --> 00:10:00.319
pure.

00:09:56.880 --> 00:10:02.959
Her countenance looked

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:04.560
average, perhaps even

00:10:02.959 --> 00:10:07.359
below

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:09.119
average.

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:11.360
I

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:16.320
tried

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:18.720
to

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:20.959
describe this to my wife, Diana, all day.

00:10:20.959 --> 00:10:26.800
She had brown eyes and

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:28.959
sandy brown hair,

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:43.839
the same color as our

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:46.320
daughter Paisley's, not

00:10:43.839 --> 00:10:49.839
like Megan's.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:53.920
She had olive

00:10:49.839 --> 00:10:57.440
skin, not white or

00:10:53.920 --> 00:11:00.560
Caucasian.

00:10:57.440 --> 00:11:02.959
Her

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:07.880
cheeks were full,

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:07.880
but she looked very plain.

00:11:09.839 --> 00:11:15.279
If you walked by her, you

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:19.560
might find

00:11:15.279 --> 00:11:19.560
her forgettable.

00:11:24.079 --> 00:11:29.120
She

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:31.600
looked very humble

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:33.040
in her demeanor and face.

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:41.519
She looked broken,

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:43.439
like a pliable

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:46.720
person. I don't know how else to say

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:48.240
it. The way her hair was and

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:50.480
everything.

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:53.279
Then I saw Jesus

00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:57.600
in the vision and he was wearing a white

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:59.519
robe with a metallic red

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:15.839
sash. He had a

00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:19.519
beautiful, vibrant, shimmery, sparkly

00:12:15.839 --> 00:12:21.440
sash on. I've never seen that before.

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:23.680
Every time it's always been purple or

00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:28.639
other colors, but this was

00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:33.040
a vibrant red sash.

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:37.360
She fell down at his feet

00:12:33.040 --> 00:12:40.399
and she was touching the nail scars in his

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:43.680
feet.

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:48.399
She put her hair and her

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:50.719
bonnet, her shawl down over her

00:12:48.399 --> 00:12:55.040
as she went for his feet and was

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:59.839
touching the nail scars in his feet.

00:12:55.040 --> 00:13:03.519
She had her hair about his feet

00:12:59.839 --> 00:13:06.320
and she was worshiping Jesus

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:08.720
in reverence

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:12.880
at his feet.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:16.560
I saw a great storm in New Orleans.

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:20.720
I saw a great storm in the east. I saw

00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:22.560
waves—it's

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:25.920
the Gulf, but it's not right there,

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:30.638
it's further in—but I saw waves around

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:33.599
him that looked like a major storm.

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:36.560
And he said, 'Peace to the storm,'and

00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:38.240
all of a sudden that storm became

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:41.839
silent.

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:44.639
He said to me, 'Tell my people to

00:13:41.839 --> 00:13:45.760
believe me, for a wave of my glory is

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:48.079
going to come through the camera

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:50.800
tonight. If they'll believe me for it,

00:13:48.079 --> 00:13:54.638
I'll heal them what they're asking for.'I

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:57.040
saw a wave of the glory of God

00:13:54.639 --> 00:13:59.199
flow through this vision going

00:13:57.040 --> 00:14:02.880
through the lens of the camera, and the

00:13:59.199 --> 00:14:04.319
presence of the Lord filled my house.

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:05.680
He spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, what

00:14:04.320 --> 00:14:08.240
would you like to have tonight?'I

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:11.199
told him privately what I was believing

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:15.240
for, and I felt the

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:15.240
presence of the Lord fill me.

00:14:25.279 --> 00:14:31.920
As I saw Mary,

00:14:28.959 --> 00:14:35.199
she had tears in her eyes

00:14:31.920 --> 00:14:38.079
and they were streaming down her cheeks

00:14:35.199 --> 00:14:39.760
as she had her face to the Father, to

00:14:38.079 --> 00:14:42.719
Jesus.

00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:44.560
I could see Mary, and she was

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:46.320
nothing I ever pictured her to be

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:48.319
because of the statues I've seen in

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:50.560
Catholic churches.

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:56.360
She doesn't look like that.

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:56.359
Her face is more

00:14:59.120 --> 00:15:02.120
full.

00:15:03.839 --> 00:15:08.760
It wasn't skinny, but it wasn't fat;

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:14.480
it was not bony looking. She

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:17.120
didn't have a defined jawline;

00:15:14.480 --> 00:15:19.760
it was more full cheeks.

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:23.199
She reminded me of someone

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:25.040
from South

00:15:23.199 --> 00:15:28.399
America;

00:15:25.040 --> 00:15:30.079
I've seen Latino women look like

00:15:28.399 --> 00:15:32.480
that in the face. I

00:15:30.079 --> 00:15:35.839
try really

00:15:32.480 --> 00:15:37.440
hard, but I was taken back because

00:15:35.839 --> 00:15:40.079
I kept wanting to look at

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:43.680
more detail of Mother

00:15:40.079 --> 00:15:46.800
Mary. I saw her

00:15:43.680 --> 00:15:48.800
weight; I

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:54.560
told Diana she looked like she's

00:15:48.800 --> 00:15:57.279
125 pounds, maybe 130 at the most. She's

00:15:54.560 --> 00:15:59.758
about 5'5".

00:15:57.279 --> 00:16:02.079
She

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:04.079
was a little woman.

00:16:05.759 --> 00:16:12.079
Jesus was about six foot. He has

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:14.320
about a size 11 foot, the way I could

00:16:12.079 --> 00:16:17.519
see it.

00:16:14.320 --> 00:16:20.000
So she came up to

00:16:17.519 --> 00:16:22.959
right underneath him.

00:16:20.000 --> 00:16:25.440
As she fell down to his

00:16:22.959 --> 00:16:30.439
feet,

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:30.440
it was something to behold.

00:16:30.880 --> 00:16:35.199
When I have visions like that—I

00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:37.359
told Diana when I was allowed to go

00:16:35.199 --> 00:16:40.639
into the garden

00:16:37.360 --> 00:16:43.279
and I saw Adam and Eve—I tried to

00:16:40.639 --> 00:16:45.120
describe them the best I could.

00:16:43.279 --> 00:16:48.959
I said, 'She looked nothing like

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:50.639
Eve. Eve's eyes were

00:16:48.959 --> 00:16:52.880
a color I've

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:55.920
never seen before.'Adam

00:16:52.880 --> 00:16:59.759
looked

00:16:55.920 --> 00:17:02.479
very chiseled; he had no

00:16:59.759 --> 00:17:04.640
fat on him. His beard

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:07.959
was perfect. Everything was perfect

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:07.959
about Adam and

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:13.839
Eve.

00:17:11.760 --> 00:17:16.079
But this was something I've

00:17:13.839 --> 00:17:18.399
never seen before.

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:24.480
As I was

00:17:21.359 --> 00:17:27.520
looking at Mother Mary, I was

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:30.000
taken back by it. I saw the way the

00:17:27.520 --> 00:17:33.760
Lord looked at it and he

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:37.280
said, 'A Judas will rise in America.'He

00:17:33.760 --> 00:17:41.120
spoke about a certain individual

00:17:37.280 --> 00:17:43.678
and I saw him have anti-Semitism deep

00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:47.520
inside his heart toward

00:17:43.679 --> 00:17:52.240
the Jewish people.

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:58.799
You will see the true person come

00:17:55.280 --> 00:18:04.360
out even more in the days ahead.

00:17:58.799 --> 00:18:04.360
The Lord said he is a Judas,

00:18:10.080 --> 00:18:13.720
a true Judas,

00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:24.240
worse than

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:29.520
Pence.

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:31.280
I'm not trying to

00:18:29.520 --> 00:18:33.360
tick anyone off, I'm just repeating

